## Lessons
- When changing a status badge in one place, check ALL places showing that status.
- Use shared CSS classes (`.pt-safe`) instead of one-off styles.
- Always test build before committing.
- Phone browser (Netlify) and Cursor browser (localhost) have separate localStorage.
- Chinese IT staff instructions should be written in Chinese.
